HedgeFusion
│
├── BRAIN (9 AI Agents)
│   ├── Analyst Team (run in parallel, ~60 sec)
│   │   ├── Fundamentals  → P/E, ROE, DCF, balance sheet
│   │   ├── Technical     → RSI, MACD, 200 DMA, Supertrend
│   │   ├── Sentiment     → FII/DII flows, bulk deals, news tone
│   │   └── News          → RBI/SEBI macro, sector events, catalysts
│   │
│   ├── Research Team (debate layer, ~90 sec)
│   │   ├── Bull Researcher  → builds strongest buy case
│   │   ├── Bear Researcher  → builds strongest bear case
│   │   └── Research Manager → adjudicates → BUY/SELL/HOLD + PASS/BLOCK
│   │
│   └── Execution Team (gate layer, ~60 sec)
│       ├── Trader          → generates exact Kite order params
│       ├── Risk Manager    → validates qty, R:R, sector limits
│       └── Portfolio Mgr   → final APPROVE or VETO
│
├── DATA FEEDS (no API key needed)
│   ├── yfinance          → live NSE prices, OHLCV, fundamentals
│   ├── NSE RSS feeds     → ET, Moneycontrol, Business Standard, RBI
│   └── NSE APIs          → FII/DII flows, bulk deals, shareholding
│
├── EXECUTION
│   ├── Paper mode        → logs to CSV, zero real money
│   └── Live mode         → Zerodha Kite Connect (when ready)
│
└── TOOLS (10 standalone modules)
    ├── hf.py                → unified command hub
    ├── portfolio_runner.py  → run all 10 holdings at once
    ├── multibagger_screener → scan 80 NSE stocks for 2x-5x candidates
    ├── fii_dii_dashboard    → institutional flow intelligence
    ├── backtester.py        → test signals on historical data
    ├── risk_dashboard.py    → VaR, concentration, drawdown
    ├── sector_rotation.py   → track where smart money flows
    ├── earnings_calendar    → upcoming results + pre-earnings briefs
    ├── watchlist.py         → BUY ZONE scanner for target stocks
    ├── trade_journal.py     → P&L tracker and agent accuracy log
    ├── alert_system.py      → Telegram / Gmail / WhatsApp alerts
    └── scheduler.py         → autonomous 9:30 AM IST daily runner


What it is NOT: A get-rich-quick system. It is a research and analysis platform that replicates what a small hedge fund analyst 
team does — gathering data, debating, sizing positions, and gatekeeping orders — but powered by AI instead of humans.